sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.NHTaskGlideAjax</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>NHTaskGlideAjax</name><script><![CDATA[var NHTaskGlideAjax = Class.create();
NHTaskGlideAjax.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {

    getCIInfo: function() {
        var fields = ['name', 'operational_status', 'owned_by', 'sys_updated_on', 'sys_updated_by'];
        var answer = '';
        var ciSysID = this.getParameter('sysparm_ci');
        var cmdbCI = new GlideRecord("cmdb_ci");
        cmdbCI.get(ciSysID);

        for (var i = 0; i < fields.length; i++) {
            answer += '\n' + cmdbCI[fields[i]].getLabel() + ': ' + cmdbCI[fields[i]].getDisplayValue();
        }
        return answer;
    },

    type: 'NHTaskGlideAjax'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2020-08-17 23:23:34</sys_created_on><sys_id>f9353f7f2f2e101070931e282799b618</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>NHTaskGlideAjax</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_f9353f7f2f2e101070931e282799b618</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-08-17 23:29:10</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
